    category as Beneficence
    priority as 6
    scope as Universal
    applicability as list containing create_universal_applicability()
    ethical_framework as Consequentialist
    legal_basis as list containing

Process called "create_constitutional_articles" returns List[ConstitutionalArticle]:
    Let articles be list containing Add create_rights_article() to articles
    Add create_duties_article() to articles
    Add create_governance_article() to articles
    Add create_enforcement_article() to articles Return articles

