Note: Validation and compliance checking
Process called "validate_constitutional_compliance" that takes constitution as Constitution and system_specification as SystemSpecification returns ComplianceResult:
    Let compliance_checks be list containing Note: Check each principle for compliance
    For each principle in constitution.principles:
    Let principle_compliance be check_principle_compliance with principle as principle and specification as system_specification
    Add principle_compliance to compliance_checks Note: Check each article for compliance For each article in constitution.articles:
    Let article_compliance be check_article_compliance with article as article and specification as system_specification
    Add article_compliance to compliance_checks Let overall_compliance be calculate_overall_compliance with checks as compliance_checks Return ComplianceResult with:
    result_id as generate_unique_id with prefix as "COMP"
    constitution_id as constitution.constitution_id
    system_id as system_specification.system_id
    compliance_level as overall_compliance.level
    compliance_score as overall_compliance.score
    individual_checks as compliance_checks
    violations as extract_violations with checks as compliance_checks
    recommendations as generate_recommendations with checks as compliance_checks
    assessment_date as DateTime.now()

